item.title: HelloWorld
item.description: Hi there. Welcome to my new blog. I’m Max and I do programming and music and stuff, so thats the kinda content you’ll find on this blog I have strong interests in both low/systems level and web stack programming so you’ll see a mix of that in languages such as python, go, and rust. If you want to take a look at some of my previous projects my github is a great place for that.
